  <brief_title>Carbohydrates to Prevent Hypoglycaemia During Physical Activity in Patients With Type 1 Diabetes</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Randomized Trial Testing Different Regimens of Carbohydrate Administration to Prevent Hypoglycaemia During a Standardized Bout of Moderate Physical Activity in Patients With Type 1 Diabetes</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Michael A. Nauck</agency>
